<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Gluten-Free Café Menu</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f1ea;
            color: #4e342e;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #6d4c41;
            color: white;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .menu-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #795548;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #6d4c41;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .menu-item {
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #ccc;
        }
        .menu-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .menu-item h3 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #5d4037;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .menu-item p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        Gluten-Free Café Menu
    </header>

    <div class="menu-container">
        <h2>Breakfast & Snacks</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Gluten-Free Pancakes <span>₹250</span></h3>
            <p>Made with almond or oat flour, these pancakes are fluffy and delicious.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Chia Pudding <span>₹180</span></h3>
            <p>A creamy, nutrient-packed pudding made with chia seeds and almond or coconut milk.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Egg Muffins <span>₹200</span></h3>
            <p>Mini baked omelets with veggies and cheese, perfect for a grab-and-go meal.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Smoothie Bowls <span>₹220</span></h3>
            <p>Thick fruit smoothies topped with nuts, seeds, and fresh fruits.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Rice Cakes with Peanut Butter & Banana <span>₹150</span></h3>
            <p>A light and crunchy snack, naturally gluten-free.</p>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Desserts & Sweets</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Flourless Chocolate Cake <span>₹280</span></h3>
            <p>A rich, fudgy cake made with cocoa, eggs, and butter.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Coconut Macaroons <span>₹160</span></h3>
            <p>Sweet and chewy cookies made from shredded coconut and egg whites.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Gluten-Free Brownies <span>₹220</span></h3>
            <p>Made with almond or coconut flour for a chewy, chocolatey bite.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Rice Pudding <span>₹180</span></h3>
            <p>A creamy dessert made with rice, milk, and a touch of vanilla or cinnamon.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Fruit & Yogurt Parfait <span>₹200</span></h3>
            <p>Layers of yogurt, fresh fruits, and gluten-free granola.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
